Module com.example.softmeth_project3
Package com.example.softmeth_project3

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
com.example.softmeth_project3.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Represents a fitness class with name, instructor, time, and members. Includes constructors, member search, add, and drop functionalities.
Author:
William Chen, Kalrav Pandit
